Run:  venv/bin/python bin/hugpy-todo-keeper
Env:  HUGPY_CENTRAL             default http://127.0.0.1:7002
      HUGPY_TODO_KEEPER_MODEL   default Qwen2.5-3B-Instruct-GGUF
      HUGPY_TODO_KEEPER_STATE   default ~/.config/hugpy/todo-keeper.json
      HUGPY_API_KEY             only needed if the site key policy is ON
"""
